# Portfolio Tracker Database Migrations

This directory contains Alembic database migration scripts for the Portfolio Tracker application.

## Structure

- `env.py`: Configuration for Alembic environment
- `script.py.mako`: Template for generating migration scripts
- `versions/`: Directory containing individual migration scripts

## Usage

### Generate a New Migration

```bash
# Generate a migration with automatic detection of changes
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Description of changes"
```

### Apply Migrations

```bash
# Apply all pending migrations
alembic upgrade head

# Apply specific number of migrations
alembic upgrade +1

# Rollback migrations
alembic downgrade -1
alembic downgrade base  # Roll back all migrations
```

### View Migration Information

```bash
# Show current migration version
alembic current

# Show migration history
alembic history --verbose
```
